  "proposed_final_antenna_rationale": "The paper's main proposed design is the single rectangular microstrip patch antenna shown as Figure 1 and parameterized in Table 1. The beam-shaping discussion comes later and explicitly combines several antennas into an array for sectorized directional use, so it is secondary to the core proposed antenna. The conclusion reports the key performance of the proposed antenna itself, which supports selecting the single-element patch as the canonical final design.",
